==============================================================================================
IF PROBLEMS IN COMPILATION WE SUGGEST TO FOLLOW THESE STEPS:

	- FIRST COMPILE KROME PACKAGE
          	ifort -O3 -c opkda1.F opkda2.F opkdmain.F krome_user_commons.F90 krome_all.F90
        - SECOND:
          	make (using the enzo Makefile)
        - THIRDH:
                Following solver tolerances are strongly suggested:
		RTOL=1e-6, ATOL=1e-10 which provide enough accuracy for ENZO. 
